1.0.0-alpha9.name: drupal/elasticsearch_connector_easy_install

security-coverage.message: Project has not opted into security advisory coverage!

1.0.0-alpha9.description:
If you are not familiar with composer and don't know how to 
install libraries but you just want to click and install everything required
the module is just for you. It contains all required by elasticsearch connector
module libraries.
